        <item>
            <title>AirPods 4 蛇年特别版登场，送 Apple 利是封 + 实物抢先睇</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/04/special-edition-airpods-4/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=special-edition-airpods-4</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/04/special-edition-airpods-4/mobile-music/headphones/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 04 Jan 2025 02:05:07 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流动音乐]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[音乐耳机]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AirPods 4]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[蛇年]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1285054</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Apple 于 2025 年 1 月 4 日推出 AirPods 4 蛇年特别限量版，现已于 Apple Store 零售店及 Apple Online Store 正式开售。每位顾客限购两副，产品数量有限，售完即止。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285064" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc04586-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc04586-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc04586-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285059" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/1-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/1-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/1.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/1-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285060" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285061" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/3-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/3-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/3.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/3-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285062" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/4-1-579x580.jpg" alt="" width="579" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/4-1-579x580.jpg 579w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/4-1.jpg 899w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/4-1-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 579px" /></p><p>这款特别版 AirPods 4 以蛇年为主题，设计灵感来自传统中国装饰艺术。耳机外壳上刻有蛇缠绕如意的图案，寓意好运及新年愿望的实现，完美契合新春氛围。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285066" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc04590-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc04590-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc04590-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285069" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/5-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/5-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/5.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/5-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p>AirPods 4 耳机附随新春利是封，这套利是封用上 Apple 苹果作为图案，背面则有由蛇形 Apple 图案，印有「叱咤迎新年」字句，一套只有 6 个，收到的朋友一定十分开心。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285067" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc04588-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc04588-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc04588-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>这已是 Apple 连续第五年推出农历新年特别版产品，在日本有 AirTag 蛇年特别版，而在大中华地区则推出特别版 AirPods 4。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285065" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc04584-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc04584-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc04584-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/01/04/special-edition-airpods-4/mobile-music/headphones/">AirPods 4 蛇年特别版登场，送 Apple 利是封 + 实物抢先睇</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
