            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Alipay HK]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AlipayHK]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1285082</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">由 2025 年 1 月起，AlipayHK 用户可透过 AlipayHK「交通」内的易乘码缴付车资，符合资格的交易将自动记录于 AlipayHK 帐户，无需额外登记。用户可以预先启动 App 内「自动领取」功能，每月 16 日自动补贴将会自动存入账户余额，毋须拍卡排队，更无需担心逾期未领取补贴。</span></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010355443.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284994" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010355443-567x580.jpg" alt="" width="567" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010355443-567x580.jpg 567w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010355443.jpg 879w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 567px" /></a></p><h2><b>用 AlipayHK 领取补贴的四大好处</b></h2><h2><b>1. 独家自动领取功能</b></h2><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">一链启动「自动领取」后，以后每月 16 日补贴会自动存入帐户余额，毋须拍卡或排队。补贴自动存入账户余额后，即可作消费、搭车等用途，非常方便！</span></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010321806.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284898" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010321806-694x388.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010321806-694x388.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010321806.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><br /><b>
]]>
